{"tid":513011,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【朱經緯判刑】撐警大聯盟的成員：今晚我哋慶祝","createTime":"2017-12-29T06:04:44.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-29T06:25:28.000Z","uid":39464,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"7c36aaabe2857a9136a66366d1d6cd2340f032b7","tid":513011,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-29T06:04:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20171229/large/1514526589_4d62.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20171229%2Flarge%2F1514526589_4d62.jpg&h=2a3a63e9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n【13：30】<br />\n距離判刑還有兩小時，撐警大聯盟的成員已謹守崗位，在法院外就位並播放歌曲「男兒當自強」，但邊拍照邊謂：「今晚我哋慶祝」。<br />\n<br />\n法院門口的另一邊有另一班支持者，聲稱是普通巿民自發支持朱。一名女子拿起咪高峰大喊：「我哋過咗個好傷心嘅聖誕節同冬至，朱警司被扣押，我哋好傷心。朱警司係好正經去執法，係光復旺角。個暴徒喺facebook話落旺角打差佬，(鄭仲恆)係有意去旺角打差佬，嚴重過七警行為。朱警司只係執法，有咩錯。嗰啲黃絲真係令人傷心。司法沉淪，係咪法官講咗就算，冇根據。朱警司係合法執法，希望法官公平公正，我地會喺度靜坐，直至有判決為止。」<br />\n<br />\n但語畢約數分鐘，她再拿起咪表示要拉起冤字橫額。支持者邊拉橫額，邊說：「我哋係無言抗議」「世紀冤案呀」。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20171229/57638601\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20171229%2F57638601&d=HT%2BmosxtFQmebK13LlDiksmB%2BETtKD6oVAJ%2Bxq8xWyI%3D&h=551daafe\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20171229%2F57638601&h=24253810\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20171229/57638601</a>"},{"pid":"88468e1030c01edf7971a77b79d9c43bef63a163","tid":513011,"uid":125357,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-29T06:08:39.000Z","msg":"今晚出左糧去慶祝<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6aec6964b23a781c98f0acc54fabd5c71ac90d52","tid":513011,"uid":15945,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-29T06:10:43.000Z","msg":"判13+3果陣就抵死判得好、無政治考慮<br />\n判豬經緯就世紀大冤案<br />\n比埋個官你做好無<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7770b9af73ed997f404239b0ec98192db68c33e7","tid":513011,"uid":28195,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-29T06:14:55.000Z","msg":"朱Sir唐庭上自辯d答案算唔算經典？"},{"pid":"197e953be3bcbb1f25aa8f2d3c55f6ffd97fdd9f","tid":513011,"uid":49609,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-29T06:25:28.000Z","msg":"點會係法官講咗就算呢, 佢又唔係人大常委<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}